Package: ggped
Type: Package
Title: Draw Pedigree Charts Using ggplot2 and kinship2
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Moritz", "Lindner", role = "aut"),
    person("Shuai", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A set of functions and geoms to draw pedigree charts from pedigree 
    data created with kinship2. Supports multi-feature segmented symbols with
    independent continuous or discrete color mapping per feature.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
